author: William A.
title: Rep. Maxine Waters chants: ‘No ban, no wall! You build it up, we’ll tear it down!’
text:
Rep. Maxine Waters chants: ‘No ban, no wall! You build it up, we’ll tear it down!’ Posted at 7:37 pm on January 29, 2017 by William A. 
This happened on Sunday during the protests: No ban, no wall! You build it up, we'll tear it down! https://t.co/uNQEkqL92o 
— Maxine Waters (@MaxineWaters) January 29, 2017 Congresswoman @MaxineWaters is here at LAX protest leading the crowd in the chant "no ban, no wall, you build it up we'll tear it down" pic.twitter.com/iNEmkVVkmW 
— Javier Panzar (@jpanzar) January 29, 2017 @realDonaldTrump This is not a reality show. Your actions have consequences in the U.S. & around the world. Governing is serious business! pic.twitter.com/ffet5zcXVS 
— Maxine Waters (@MaxineWaters) January 29, 2017 CA congresswoman Maxine Waters joins protesters. Says Dems need to make Trump, GOP know they can't away with "any old thing they want to" pic.twitter.com/Or2lRAGHd6 
— Josie Huang (@josie_huang) January 29, 2017 
Reaction: @jpanzar @MaxineWaters Even our political leaders are on the ground fighting Fascism. When will the Radical "Christian" Right hear? 
— Michael Lummus (@michael_lummus) January 29, 2017 @jpanzar @LynnRoseberry @MaxineWaters Take it straight to Trump-GOP remind them Impeachment & Malfeasance is only a matter of Public Disgust
